!v702!C:\SciELO\Serial\rsp\v38n5\markup\21757.htm
!v704!<p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Compuseram as vari&aacute;veis    do subgrupo sociodemogr&aacute;fico: sexo, idade, cor, escolaridade e estado    civil.</font></p>     ^cY
!v705!S
!v706!p
!v708!130
!v709!article
!v880!S0034-89102004000500011
!v882!^v38^n5
!v936!^i0034-8910^y2004^o5
!ID 0000048
